The '''''Kur-hashan''''' was the [[Command ship/Legends|command ship]] of [[B'shith Vorrik]]. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], it participated in the [[Battle of Bastion]], [[Battle of Borosk (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Borosk]], [[Battle of Yaga Minor (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Yaga Minor]], and [[Battle of Esfandia]]. It was damaged at [[Esfandia/Legends|Esfandia]], and with a Vong defeat ensured, Vorrik attempted to ram the ''Kur-hashan'' into the [[Right to Rule|enemy command ship]]. However, the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] destroyed the ''Kur-hashan'' before it came close, killing everyone aboard.

==Behind the scenes==
Described variously as a "destroyer" and a "[[Warship/Legends|warship]]," the ''Kur-hashan'' may have been a [[Miid ro'ik|''Miid Ro'ik'']]/[[destroyer]] analog.

